headline: Wells Fargo sees recovery in specialty retail, upgrades Bath & Body Works
summary: Investing.com -- Wells Fargo forecast a stable consumer backdrop in 2025, supported by healthy U.S. demand, a strong holiday season, and stabilizing European trends, according to its retail sector outlook.
